SquareRoot is

  sqrt(a i32) i32
    pre
      a ≥ 0
    post
      (result * result ≤ a) && ((result+1) * (result+1) > a)
  =>
    for res := 1, (res + a / res) / 2
        it in 0..99
    until (( res    *  res    ≤ a) &&
           ((res+1) * (res+1) > a)    )
      res
    else
      panic "*** error, sqrt diverges"

  say "sqrt(16) = {sqrt(16)}"
  say "sqrt(81) = {sqrt(81)}"
  say "sqrt(-16) = {sqrt(-16)}" // 1. should flag an error, precondition failed
